<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EJS 3</title>

    <style>
        figure {
            border: 2px solid black;
        }
        footer, header {
            align-items: center;
            border: 2px solid black;
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 50px;
            padding: 5px;
        }
        img {
            max-height: 50px;
            max-width: auto;
        }
        .database {
            background-color: lightgrey;
            /* color: white; */
            margin: 5px;
            padding: 5px;
        }
        .database-name {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            text-align: center;
        }
        figure, .images {
            align-items: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 5px;
            padding: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("header") %>


    <h1>EJS, example 3</h1>
    <p>This is the main EJS template.</p>

    <div class="images">
        <figure>
            <!---->
            <img src="http://icons.iconarchive.com/icons/goescat/macaron/256/gimp-icon.png" alt="Remote Image">
            <figcaption>Remote image</figcaption>
        </figure>
    
        <figure>
            <!--http://icons.iconarchive.com/icons/goescat/macaron/256/firefox-icon.png-->
            <img src="img/firefox-icon.png" alt="Local Image">
            <figcaption>Local image</figcaption>
        </figure>
    </div>

    <p>The items below come from a MySQL database.</p>

    <p><strong>If nothing shows up in black boxes below</strong>, go back to the main page of the app and populate the database.</p>

    <div>
        <% for (let i of post) { %>
            <div class="database">
                <p class="database-name">
                    
                    <a href="/get-post/<%= i.id %>" title="<%= i.title %>">
                        <%= i.title %>: ID <%= i.id %>
                    </a>

                </p>
                <p><%= i.body %></p>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
    
    <%- include("footer") %>
    <script src="js/random-message.js"></script>
</body>
</html>


